Usage: placeBondPad [-help] [-fix] [-pad <padName>] [-pinName <pinName>]
                    [-position {I M O}] {-ioInstName <instName> | -selected }

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-fix                       # assigns a fixed status to the specified bond pad
                           # (bool, optional)
-ioInstName <instName>     # specifies the name of I/O instance
                           # (string, required)
-pad <padName>             # specifies the name of bond pad (string, optional)
-pinName <pinName>         # specifies the name of the pin inside the instance
                           # (string, optional)
-position {I M O}          # defines the stagger position of the specified bond
                           # pad (enum, optional)
-selected                  # places selected bond pad on the specified I/O
                           # instance (bool, required)